1114
01:14:59,625 --> 01:15:01,458
"The theatre shakes with
roaring joy and screams,"

1115
01:15:01,542 --> 01:15:02,792
"Once the heater sets the scene,"

1116
01:15:02,833 --> 01:15:03,542
"BANG! BANG!"

1117
