"BANG! BANG!"

1122
01:15:46,625 --> 01:15:52,417
"After falling for you,
I'm not the one I used to be,"

1123
01:15:53,875 --> 01:16:00,500
"After falling for you,
I'm not the one I used to be,"

1124
01:16:00,583 --> 01:16:08,417
"Now I wait down your lane,
